name: label-maker-dask
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "label-maker-dask" %}
{% set version = "0.1.2" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/label-maker-dask-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a1765ae33548b10bb65ebd18922657e22c864566c87e9a9309fa85379637fd51

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - dask-core
    - mapbox-vector-tile
    - mercantile
    - numpy
    - pillow
    - python >=3.6
    - rasterio
    - requests
    - rio-tiler >=2
    - shapely

test:
  imports:
    - label_maker_dask
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/developmentseed/label-maker-dask
  summary: Run label maker as a dask job
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - drewbo
